text: Thomas Fuchs (born 10 November 1957) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zürich
